Detailed Description

template<class SetsType, class DataStructDB, class Container = vector<SetsType>>
class ItBinaryDB< SetsType, DataStructDB, Container >

Iterator on a BinaryDB.

The template parameter SetsType is the type of the element stored in the db. The template parameter DataStructDB is the type of the data structure storing the db. The template parameter Container is the container used to store the transactions.

See also:
BinaryDB.
